This paper is likely to belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) category as it deals with the monitoring and management of large-scale cloud data centers. It also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) categories. The paper also discusses the classification of VMs, which falls under the Systems and Control (cs.SY) category. Finally, the paper involves the evaluation of the proposed approach, which could be considered as a form of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) evaluation.
